{"tid":1364721,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"何妖一辣著誰就連墓碑也都扑碎","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:35:55.000Z","uid":33418,"like":368,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"0d15d558ab876dfeb86a74cf04922c6667b8198a","tid":1364721,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:14:36.000Z","msg":"快落去　每日也在望著親母鬧佢<br />\n望墳墓    亦難望黑幫看守佢<br />\n快落去　老豆亦扑佢<br />\n<br />\n跪墳墓    跪墳墓<br />\n跪求娘親不發怒<br />\n盡孝但掃墓忘了做到<br />\n就如阿堯日前在記招已失控<br />\n就是這樣孝義　誰不快<br />\n<br />\n#扮哂激動便流淚<br />\n碰上了中共便陶醉<br />\n活著是為了望墳墓狂揼碎<br />\n害怕追殺便疑慮<br />\n怕過於濕滑便離去<br />\n活著未盡孝　是誰"},{"pid":"225a135e13a8e04700bf5026f7d754698daba447","tid":1364721,"uid":242537,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢首淨記得濕曬死肥仔"},{"pid":"cf2e4c760c1edc2a3e00e10f1a12de1c7d763d9f","tid":1364721,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class